text: Zhala Mahsimova (born 2 September 1996) is an Azerbaijani footballer who plays as a midfielder for the Azerbaijan women's national team. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Azerbaijani women's footballers Category:Azerbaijan women's international footballers Category:Russian Women's Football Championship players Category:Azerbaijani expatriate footballers Category:Azerbaijani expatriate sportspeople in Russia Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Russia Category:ZFK Zenit Saint Petersburg players
